text: Barbara Matić (born 3 December 1994 in Split, Croatia) is a Croatian judoka. A two-time world junior champion in the women's 70 kg division, Matić won bronze at the 2014 European Judo Championships. Her younger sister Brigita Matić has also been a successful judoka on junior level.
